                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote>Sephardi semi-cursive scripts. Items 1-2 (ff. 1-96) and 4 (ff.
                                175v-254v) by the same hand on paper with the same watermarks. Item 3 (ff.
                                97-174) by a different hand on different paper. Item 5 (ff. 255-284 by
                                another hand, or perhaps two hands; fol. 284v was completed in a cursive
                                script.</handNote>
                            
